snippet.title: Tacoma Announce Trailer for Xbox One
snippet.description: Discovery. Exploration. Isolation. What is life like 200,000 miles from Earth? Uncover the mysteries held by Lunar Transfer Station Tacoma and its crew, living at the edge of humanity's reach. Tacoma, the next game from the creators of “Gone Home." First on console on Xbox One.
